OL,3,CFrom Brighton with Love: The Body
OL,4,CShop's rise and fall from one seaside
OL,5,Cstore
OL,7,FA small shop on a bustling Brighton
OL,8,Fbackstreet is where it all began on 27
OL,9,FMarch 1976.
OL,11,FFounder Dame Anita Roddick's unique
OL,12,Frecipe of natural cosmetics with a
OL,13,Fsocial conscience would prove an
OL,14,Finstant hit with customers, setting in
OL,15,Fmotion the growth of a global beauty
OL,16,Fbrand.
OL,18,FThe Body Shop would expand to
OL,19,Fencompass more than 3,000 stores in 70
OL,20,Fcountries.
