OL,3,CFrom Brighton with Love: The Body
OL,4,CShop's rise and fall from one seaside
OL,5,Cstore
OL,7,FAt its core was a simple idea:
OL,8,Fskincare products made from natural
OL,9,Fingredients, sold with limited
OL,10,Fpackaging and without testing on
OL,11,Fanimals.
OL,13,F"I have great pleasure in breaking
OL,14,Frules. Breaking the rules of the
OL,15,Findustry that I'm involved in," Dame
OL,16,FAnita told ITV News in 1984.
OL,18,FThe pioneering businesswoman was born
OL,19,Fin Littlehampton in 1942 and would go
OL,20,Fon to establish the Body Shop's head
OL,21,Foffice in the Sussex seaside town.
