OL,7,FThe company was floated on the London
OL,8,FStock Exchange in the 1980s, and would
OL,9,Fremain publicly listed until it was
OL,10,Fbought by L'Oreal in 2006.
OL,12,FThe deal attracted controversy because
OL,13,Fof the French company's previous
OL,14,Fstance on a range of ethical issues,
OL,15,Fincluding animal testing.
OL,17,FDame Anita died in 2007, aged 64,
OL,18,Fafter suffering a brain haemorrhage.
