OL,7,FFamily friend and co-founder of the
OL,8,FBig Issue magazine, Lord Bird, said
OL,9,Fthe Body Shop never recovered from the
OL,10,Fchange of leadership.
OL,12,F"Sometimes, when you have a really,
OL,13,Freally powerful person who runs a
OL,14,Fbusiness and is always innovating,
OL,15,Falways bringing about change, and then
OL,16,Fthey hit health problems ` and then
OL,17,Fdie prematurely ` the business finds
OL,18,Fit very difficult because it was a
OL,19,Fpersonality-driven business," he added.
