OL,10,Fdo better for the environment and for
OL,11,Ftheir suppliers and for the people
OL,12,Fthey source from."
OL,14,FThe Body Shop's UK division was last
OL,15,Fweek, just months after the latest
OL,16,Fowners ` global private equity group
OL,17,FAurelius ` took control of the company.
